    "title": "wallet: balance gone when tx broadcast failed",
    "body": "on BTC mainnet. I set the txfee as minimal (custom `0.00001` per kilo) and it failed. The problem is displaying my balance as `0` (on QT GUI side) until abandon this tx. I was very scared.\r\n\r\nv0.20.1\r\n\r\n```\r\n2021-01-15T09:26:27Z [default wallet] AddToWallet xxx  new\r\n2021-01-15T09:26:28Z [default wallet] Submitting wtx xxx to mempool for relay\r\n2021-01-15T09:26:28Z [default wallet] CommitTransaction(): Transaction cannot be broadcast immediately, mempool min fee not met, 142 < 152\r\n2021-01-15T09:29:10Z [default wallet] Fee Calculation: Fee:17407 Bytes:142 Needed:17407 Tgt:0 (requested 0) Reason:\"PayTxFee set\" Decay 0.00000: Estimation: (-1 - -1) -nan% 0.0/(0.0 0 mem 0.0 out) Fail: (-1 - -1) -nan% 0.0/(0.0 0 mem 0.0 out)\r\n```\r\n",
